        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Gas leak check</strong><p>All pipework and appliance connections tested for gas leaks using calibrated detection equipment. Any leak found is classified using the Gas Industry Unsafe Situations Procedure and addressed before we leave.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Flue integrity and combustion products</strong><p>Flues tested for integrity, correct sealing and safe discharge of combustion gases. A damaged or blocked flue causes carbon monoxide to build up inside the property.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Ventilation adequacy</strong><p>All gas appliances checked for adequate ventilation as specified by the manufacturer. Blocked or inadequate ventilation is a common cause of incomplete combustion and carbon monoxide risk.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Safety device operation</strong><p>All appliance safety devices tested including flame failure devices, pressure relief valves and overheat cut-outs. Each must demonstrate correct operation before the appliance can pass the inspection.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Signs of incomplete combustion</strong><p>Checked for staining, sooting or carbon deposits around appliances. These indicate a combustion problem and potential carbon monoxide risk that must be resolved before the certificate is issued.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>All gas appliances in the property</strong><p>Every gas appliance inspected individually, including boiler, gas fires, gas hobs, cookers and any other gas-connected appliances. All recorded separately on the CP12.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>CP12 certificate issued and emailed same day</strong><p>On completion, the CP12 is issued digitally and emailed the same day. Includes the engineer's Gas Safe registration number, inspection date and result for every appliance checked.</p></div></div>
